column8: Cloudy. Medium (60%) chance of snow showers, most likely during this afternoon and evening. Winds southeasterly 30 to 45 km/h.
Cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of snow showers. Winds southeasterly 30 to 45 km/h.
Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers or snow. Winds east to southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h.

Partly cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late morning and afternoon. Winds easterly 15 to 20 km/h becoming light during the morning.
Partly cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Winds easterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to southwesterly during the morning.
Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm. Winds northerly 15 to 20 km/h shifting southeasterly 20 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. Winds southeasterly 25 to 30 km/h decreasing to 15 to 20 km/h during the day.
